            <h3>11.Shanmuganathi Dam</h3>
  </div>
   <div class="card-body">
     <h5>  Shanmuganathi Dam is
        located amidst the greens of Malabar Hills,the Dam and its adjacent
         rippling water create a lovely ambience for a day out or a picnic.  </h5>
<p>
  Shanmuganathi Dam  is a lifeline for the drylands to all agricultural villages of Theni.
  There is a Shanmugha Temple nearby within 1 kilometre, where resides an idol of Lord Murugan.
   You can visit that if you have time and pay your respects.
</p>
